to come back.

76
00:08:35.650 --> 00:08:37.918
<i>You think he was</i>
<i>spying on you?</i>

77
00:08:37.953 --> 00:08:39.553
<i>No. not spying.</i>

78
00:08:39.588 --> 00:08:41.856
<i>The Dothraki think</i>
<i>outsiders are ridiculous</i>

79
00:08:41.890 --> 00:08:43.357
taking shame
in the naked body.

80
00:08:43.391 --> 00:08:46.727
They make love under the stars
for the whole khalasar to see.

81
00:08:48.263 --> 00:08:50.431
Yes. Your Grace.

82
00:08:50.465 --> 00:08:52.766
But you are not
Dothraki.

83
00:08:52.801 --> 00:08:54.768
No.

84
00:08:56.271 --> 00:08:58.138
Well. I don't see
