87
00:09:04.980 --> 00:09:07.281
He was interested.

88
00:09:07.315 --> 00:09:09.884
What?

89
00:09:11.186 --> 00:09:14.388
I believe he was
interested.

90
00:09:16.191 --> 00:09:18.259
When the slavers
